{
    "headline": "Oxtails with Gravy",
    "name": "Oxtails with Gravy",
    "description": "This oxtail recipe is so flavorful from beef oxtail simmered slowly in a savory broth, then cooked in a delicious gravy until fall-of-the-bone tender.",
